  "description": "<b>昨天一大早，30岁的杨先生蹲在马桶上玩ipad，起身时突然一阵眩晕，扑通一下跌倒在卫生间里。经诊断，他因长期久蹲马桶患上血栓性外痔，长期便血以致起身时晕倒。</b> 杨先生是个软件工程师，前不久，他新买了台ipad玩上了瘾，坐地铁、走路都拿在手上，连上厕所的时间都不放过。这两个月，每天早晨闹铃一响，他就起床拿着ipad去卫生间，坐在马桶上看新闻、玩游戏，一蹲就是个把小时。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d6251a6/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241401.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%85%E8%B9%B2%E9%A9%AC%E6%A1%B6%E7%8E%A9iPad+%E6%82%A3%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B%E9%97%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241401.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%85%E8%B9%B2%E9%A9%AC%E6%A1%B6%E7%8E%A9iPad+%E6%82%A3%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B%E9%97%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241401.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%85%E8%B9%B2%E9%A9%AC%E6%A1%B6%E7%8E%A9iPad+%E6%82%A3%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B%E9%97%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241401.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%85%E8%B9%B2%E9%A9%AC%E6%A1%B6%E7%8E%A9iPad+%E6%82%A3%E7%97%94%E7%96%AE%E6%99%95%E5%80%92%E5%9C%A8%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B%E9%97%B4\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Fart